    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择游玩风格</h2>有四个特点鲜明且技能值各异的角色以供选择 - 弓箭手、火枪手、探索者或战士，每个角色都拥有不同的天赋专长。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1664580/extras/36f20b510992bb19cf0eb338db029d11.poster.avif?t=1726557690\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1664580/extras/36f20b510992bb19cf0eb338db029d11.webm?t=1726557690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1664580/extras/36f20b510992bb19cf0eb338db029d11.mp4?t=1726557690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >提升技能和技能值</h2>通过技能树路径、收集符文获得强力加成奖励以及提升基本技能的方式帮助角色不断成长。将点数加在爆炸物路径、攻击路径、生命路径、炼金术路径、物料路径或特有角色特有技能树分支上。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1664580/extras/4867510a1755caeb125a33320301baf2.avif?t=1726557690\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集战利品并管理物品栏</h2>运气也将决定成败。在地图上可以随机获得各种物品，也可拾取金币和银币，或寻找护甲、武器和其他物品栏物品。你还可以拜访炼金术士、铁匠、商人或裁缝，购买额外物品、进行交易或修理装备。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索幻想世界 </h2>亲身体验中世纪幻想世界。你将遇到小镇、地下洞穴、熔岩湖泊、冰天雪地、漫毒荒地、苍茫沙漠等诸多场景。进行战斗或使用学得的技能来应对各种情形。你将遭遇30种拥有不同技能和力量的敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1664580/extras/6a9d4e721b92a908bfeec0023d0c790c.poster.avif?t=1726557690\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1664580/extras/6a9d4e721b92a908bfeec0023d0c790c.webm?t=1726557690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1664580/extras/6a9d4e721b92a908bfeec0023d0c790c.mp4?t=1726557690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
